snippet.title: Super Co-op Adventure Trailer #2
snippet.description:
This is Super Co-op Adventure. A retro-ish local co-op puzzle-action-platformer videogame that everybody can play on their computer without the need of a wired/wireless gamepad. Your keyboard and mouse can do great things together...
Download Free Early Access by visiting: www.2players.it
